 		<p>Did you know that the average household throws out about 480 pounds of glass every year? Even if you donâ€™t quite meet the national average, your fridge is still probably full of sauces, beverages and condiments chilling in glass containers. Good thing there are plenty of great ideas out there for reusing them. Learn how to reuse glass bottles and jars of all shapes and sizes in simple but spectacular ways.</p>
