		<img src="img/PLASTICP2.jpg" alt="blog "/>

		<p>Help nature in two wonderful ways with this project, which both repurposes a plastic bottle and feeds backyard birds. While you might need to make a run for birdseed, all the other materials are probably already hiding in your kitchen.</p>
			
